# Monolith Platform Rules

You are working in the Monolith AI-Native Engineering Platform monorepo.

## Stack

- Turborepo + pnpm workspaces
- Next.js (web), NestJS (api), Expo (mobile)
- Prisma + PostgreSQL, Redis + BullMQ
- Vitest + Playwright

## Conventions

- Feature-based modules in `apps/api/src/features/`
- Infrastructure in `apps/api/src/infrastructure/`
- Shared UI: `@monolith/ui` (shadcn/ui)
- Shared types: `@monolith/types`
- Prisma schema at repository root: `prisma/schema.prisma`
- Docker-first local development via `docker compose`

## Rules

- Production-grade code only; no placeholder business logic unless requested
- Match existing patterns; minimise scope of changes
- Type-safe, explicit configuration
- Every PR must pass lint, typecheck, tests, and build
